title: Questions Answered: An Introduction to QAnon and the Great Awakening
description: Patriots within the Q anon movement have dedicated their lives to educating the masses, use them as a resource and heed their counsel. Pat Quincy delivers a quick, easy to read description of Q's origins and early messages. After reading this book, you will have a better understanding of how to uncover the secrets in Q's messages and where to look for guidance when you're confused about what to do next. You can't know everything but you should know where to look.WWG1WGA
author: Pat Quincy
